version_description:
ICYMI! Filto are now here to meet y’all!
We're thankful for our engineers for giving us (and you) an even better version just in time to coordinate all our very important night before Xmas plans...like staying in. Cheers to sweatpants and Filto ;)

You asked, we heard. Photo editing is available!

- Photos can be edit. Also you can convert a photo to a short video to edit.
- Watermark can be removed for Filto Pros in the Settings.
- Update carefully chose filters & effects, A LOT of it.
- Christmas filters & effects are ready for you.
- Performance improvement.
Being popular is so hard (tears), but Filto is here to help :)

Guess what?! Text can be added to Photos/ Videos! Also those fancy shadow effects can be added to photos.
Applause! Dancing! Excitement! Hugs!
-Add Text to Photos / Videos
-Change kinds of artistic fonts to add on
-Rainbow, aureole, glow, snow… and many other effects(continue updating) can be add to photos
-Holiday contents updated for you
-Bug fix and improvements
And what is the best part? We’ve only just begun… Stay tuned to discover more fun in Filto!

New Year, Same Friend (Yes, we mean us!) How about a fresh Filto-made video post for your 1st. look of 2019? Let’s do it!

- Get your hot January posts contents updated
- Enhanced some performance to make Filto fast like a Lambo (skrrt, skrrt, skrrt）
- Vacuumed all the area rugs and bugs
